
USAGE: komi k

This is used to change the komi of a game. The first time one of the players
issure this command, the new komi is offered to the other player. The other
player must then type the same command to set the komi.

Example: komi -5.5

This offers/sets the komi of 5.5 points to black.

NOTES:

  The server does not support 0.0 komi games very well.  Results are
  undefined.

  When a game is started, komi defaults to 5.5 when both players have the
  same rank or rating, and 0.5 if they differ.

SEE ALSO: match handicap

